sentences: Bob Bradley (born 5 February 1974) is a British music composer, producer and songwriter.
In 1997, Bradley signed with the newly formed V2 Records with a project called 'Lovebabies'.
They released their debut single 'Explore' in the same year.
A follow up single was released in early 1998, "Blue Earth Angel", featuring remixes from Attica Blues, Morcheeba and DJ Pulse.
In 2012, Bradley produced and arranged Above & Beyond's Acoustic album.
As of 2021, Bob has been working on his own material, developing talent and new projects with Yungblud, Jeff Beck, Ozzy Osbourne & Johnny Depp under his given name Robert Edward Bradley.
Bob Bradley was born on 5 February 1974 in Teesside, England.
